Bra att du tar upp det – just nu är din sida mer “basic webshop” än high fashion. Vi kan fixa det ganska snabbt med rätt designval.

Jag delar upp det i två delar:

🎨 Uppgradera designen (din stil: high fashion / clean / kantig)
🖼️ Hur du lägger in dina egna produktbilder (enkelt)
🎨 1. NY DESIGN (high fashion / minimalistisk)

Byt ut HELA din styles.css mot detta:

body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    color: #111;
}

/* NAVBAR */
header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    background: white;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}

header h1 {
    letter-spacing: 4px;
}

nav a {
    margin-left: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
    font-weight: 500;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
    height: 70vh;
    background: #eaeaea;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

/* PRODUKTER */
#products {
    padding: 60px 40px;
}

.filters {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.filters button {
    border: 1px solid black;
    background: white;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    margin-right: 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

/* GRID */
.product-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
}

/* PRODUKTKORT */
.product {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    transition: 0.2s;
}

.product:hover {
    border: 1px solid black;
}

/* BILDER */
.product img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 300px;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

/* KNAPP */
.product button {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid black;
    background: white;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.product button:hover {
    background: black;
    color: white;
}

/* VARUKORG */
.cart {
    position: fixed;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 320px;
    height: 100%;
    background: white;
    border-left: 2px solid black;
    padding: 20px;
}

.hidden {
    display: none;
}

